::KitKat::

She opened a link to her pack. "Fall back.  Hold your fire and fall 
back.. Megatron said he would leave, let him go if he is willing to 
do so." She walked from the lab, her clone only 25% complete.  She 
walked to the entrance and stod in the door way.  With the shields 
still up, she felt safe behind them from attack. She wanted to see 
Megatron leave with her own eyes.
